## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
1. `cd /tmp/test_clone && python3 src/ingest.py` — mora proći bez greške
2. `python3 src/dashboard.py` — mora prikazati broj fragmenata (može biti 0 ako nema podataka)
3. `python3 -c "from src.ingest import load_documents"` — import test

### Manual Verification
- Korisnik klonira repo i pokrene `pip install -r requirements.txt && python3 src/ingest.py`
